pub fn serialize_public_key(poly: &[i32; N]) -> Vec<u8>     // 896 bytes
pub fn deserialize_public_key(bytes: &[u8]) -> Option<[i32; N]>
```

**14-bit packing:** 512 coefficients × 14 bits = 7,168 bits = 896 bytes

