## Summary

The **falcon-rs** crate is a complete, production-ready Rust implementation of Falcon-512 with:

✓ Full cryptographic operations (keygen, sign, verify)
✓ Generic hash trait supporting SHAKE256 and Poseidon
✓ WASM bindings for browser use
✓ Deterministic and random signing modes
✓ SecretKey serialization/deserialization (3,584 bytes)
✓ Comprehensive testing with NIST KAT vectors
✓ snforge-compatible JSON serialization for Cairo integration

The core data flow is: Message → Hash-to-point → FFT/NTT operations → Gaussian sampling → Signature compression.

